	<title><a href="https://api.heliview.nl/">API Congress</a>, Rotterdam, NL</title>
	<presentation id="index">
		<title>How to Accelerate your API Journey</title>
		<toc class="abstract">APIs are the connective fabric of digital transformation. But they are only as useful as the capabilities they are representing, and only productive when they can be changed easily, frequently, and without the need for coordination. We look at the factors that really matter for API utility at the business level, and what it takes to change these factors when embarking on your API journey. We look at the trajectory of developing an API strategy for explicit goals, establishing an API program to realize these goals, and cultivating an API mindset across the organization.</toc>
